create_factor.Rd

Turns character vector into a factor. The labels for the levels are retrieved by joining value_labels.

Usage

create_factor(x)

Arguments

x

Character vector containing value labels from the Landesdatenbank NRW

Value

Factor using the description from value_labels

Examples

create_factor(value_labels[["value_label"]])
